  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.poster.avif?t=1774377854\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.webm?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.mp4?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this relaxing game, your ability to optimize inventory space will be put to the test. Each relic has a unique shape and its own challenges to fit, making the gameplay experience both challenging and rewarding. Relish the sense of achievement as you uncover hidden items and refine your strategy to collect all the available treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.poster.avif?t=1774377854\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.webm?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.mp4?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to find and organize all the relics in Loot Stack: Relics Hunter? Come test your skills and lose yourself in an unforgettable medieval adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/398d12c52b2de264028b412dc0b3fd3c.poster.avif?t=1774377854\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/398d12c52b2de264028b412dc0b3fd3c.webm?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/398d12c52b2de264028b412dc0b3fd3c.mp4?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.poster.avif?t=1774377854\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.webm?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.mp4?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this relaxing game, your ability to optimize inventory space will be put to the test. Each relic has a unique shape and its own challenges to fit, making the gameplay experience both challenging and rewarding. Relish the sense of achievement as you uncover hidden items and refine your strategy to collect all the available treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.poster.avif?t=1774377854\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.webm?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.mp4?t=1774377854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to find and organize all the relics in Loot Stack: Relics Hunter? Come test your skills and lose yourself in an unforgettable medieval adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img